snippet.textDisplay: WTF, Dice? Don't get me wrong. The update sounds cool and all. The ewoks and the ISB agents, they both sound awesome. Let alone the new weapons. But WHEN IS CAD BANE COMING?!?! That is literally the one thing I want to know. In HVV, BB-9E does not deserve to be next to Count Dooku. Out of all the intense and awesome heroes/villains you could have added in the game, you chose BB-8 and BB-9E. WHY?!?!?!

snippet.textDisplay:
Id like to see Galactic Assault and star fighter assault added to Instant action in the future and an increase in bots on each team to atleast 32 for single player.
If Star fighter assault is added it would be cool to see ship boarding, like a mini objective of defending your hanger from an enemy boarding.
A respawn counter for supremacy and a slider in the Instant action menu to lower or increase respawns for both teams instead of relying on just the capture points to win.
Also celebration edition should be able to be used offline, theres no reason why something I paid for cant be used without a subscription.

Utapau, Mygeeto( 21st Nova Corps skins), Coruscant, Tantive IV
Galactic assault for these maps aswell as GA for Felucia.

It would be awesome to see all the battlefront 2015 maps ported to this game, I know we have the same planets but I mean the lay outs.

And lastly an option to change Team AI skins in the instant action menu before launching the battle.

Everything so far is looking great in this game, im so happy they added option for HUD and more options in Instant action, the AI is fantastic aswell, some of the best AI ive seen in games so far, hopefully they keep up the good work and make this game a masterpiece but untill they add what I've listed I'm staying on Battlefront 2 classic lol
